{"tid":1989094,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得香港張車牌好撚柒？","createTime":"2020-04-25T16:09:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T02:48:08.000Z","uid":65658,"like":45,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4ea025b2a89556347d2b7565b1b9c6c84e0ea05b","tid":1989094,"uid":65658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T16:09:38.000Z","msg":"得張過咗膠嘅紙仔<br />\n冇相冇晶片連bar code都冇<br />\n完全無任何科技可言<br />\n連中學張學生證都先進過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n拎過俾啲外國friend睇 <br />\n佢地都笑張野好似70年代咁<br />\n人地啲車牌最少有設計 可以當身分證明文件咁用<br />\n香港政府憑乜撚野收香港人900蚊換張咁嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d128a00f8882bab6748bd9f5e5a3524257eea25c","tid":1989094,"uid":65658,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T16:13:18.000Z","msg":"英國嗰張都柒 但係最少個質地正常啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PAKKPTm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPAKKPTm.jpg&h=7b729966&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得美加嗰啲靚啲 show到當地特色 有啲代表性<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q0CkodV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ0CkodV.jpg&h=6ee17274&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WOufb7f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWOufb7f.jpg&h=00cbebee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf01da3286039e4c7169ef4a481cd849f4c498c6","tid":1989094,"uid":39012,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T16:17:40.000Z","msg":"雖然係柒 但人地唔係因為當身分證用先design到咁咩?"},{"pid":"884e1c94ace41be44d481f61d6c1a2c3e90a7e08","tid":1989094,"uid":65658,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bf01da3286039e4c7169ef4a481cd849f4c498c6","tid":1989094,"uid":39012,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T16:17:40.000Z","msg":"雖然係柒 但人地唔係因為當身分證用先design到咁咩?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T16:20:21.000Z","msg":"係呀 <br />\n但係我覺得香港都可以仿效<br />\n香港得